{"tid":2462322,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 呂布軍第二十四次股東大會，昨晚錄得史上最快最大敗仗！不足一小時即蝕10%！","createTime":"2021-03-26T02:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T02:47:32.000Z","uid":149018,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4476d74288d4e55d3eb1481ea18851428c6c273c","tid":2462322,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第二十三次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQm8XeyFSgeTEobSLgh8xY59KUxkaD1Uon65Xuwr5ELM6?filename=pepCzcV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpepCzcV.png&h=adbccaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb6bpjXfn9BcoKxWAoU85kV52WJYExU88v9uuTFL4Aqwd?filename=Q4KZNxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4KZNxV.png&h=d6462b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZWB3mGtG1yzm6iEqFMizEtxaRuE2v3aoJ5Ls2Ti8idvf?filename=fEKZNxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEKZNxV.png&h=7f3f6020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZKz5seu3tMBQkW9PpYxLtvJstNDv2qboEDG9eHu1N4ox?filename=pQFx1Gf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQFx1Gf.png&h=a6a96e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">775.34</span>HP (預計) 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-22.47</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十四波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣舖進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為呂布親領赤兔部隊。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團註明兩軍進軍方向提議<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領意見<br />\n2. 收集軍師兵士們之股票後奉先設下<span class=\"red\">點將台</span>再聽天由命買入。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計為<span class=\"red\">盤前16:00</span>。<br />\n4. 二軍赤兔隊無限期反省中，不定期再次進軍<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、盤後07:45或開市緊急調動<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位，若為QQQ 上下限改為3%。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYF8CYZdgnU2H7XkzghXoDmFVQLdkDD3Er92aqfVyg8g9?filename=4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第二十二次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呂布曰：膠龍游淺水，我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf6tqgioWybw7XGSNGzaf3aRvKPJFc7dhsiPwZL43n9Bk?filename=S5vmUU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5vmUU9.png&h=c452f2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呂布誤中奸計，武力100 智力70操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfRSmXTAtCZ99Tq4X6ddXr1JKPyqqBVQ5t3aaQbZYSYVY?filename=4vyLH8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vyLH8F.jpg&h=6f120297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9158f7e4dda1ecec67f0d07dee053788c91d7c6d","tid":2462322,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"Gme 將軍 你次次都唔聽忠言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42562afd40090b43d0974abdcd015927507ffa18","tid":2462322,"uid":2316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"幾時出隻逆向呂布ETF"},{"pid":"79971b5494f60af55dc0683044b4f4e699f85fd7","tid":2462322,"uid":298100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"大佬呀 你次次盤前高追 賭盤前都睇定D先啦"},{"pid":"f8a1dc7e101b7e9684bf6a98c92b2e8830ec3c06","tid":2462322,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"你真係搭沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" cl